action plan on freshwater is critical if freshwater resources are
to be available for people on a sustainable basis," Claude Martin,
Director-General of WWF International told a press conference here
today.
</P>
<P>
The WWF sees the Convention on Wetlands signed in 1971 and the
Convention on Biological Diversity signed in 1992 as key
freshwater-related international treaties that should be given
more attention to. 
