Environment (ACCCSWWE) opened here on Wednesday to discuss the
environmental status of the sea.
</P>
<P>
The participants at the meeting have presented 12 plans on the
weather, water and environment watch on the Caspian Sea, Iranian
official news agency IRNA reported.
</P>
<P>
