the development road of China and point out the correct way for
the nation's revitalization, says a signed article carried by
today's People's Daily.
</P>
<P>
Deng Xiaoping Theory has developed from the fact that China is
in the primary stage of socialism, the article says.
</P>
<P>
The theory has objectively and profoundly analyzed the
features, the basic conditions, the principal contradiction and
the fundamental task in the primary stage of modern China. After a
thorough understanding of the nation, Deng, the late Chinese
leader, put up a complete set of theories on building socialism
with Chinese characteristics.
</P>
<P>
Guided by Deng Xiaoping Theory, the Chinese people have in the
past two decades achieved great successes, it says.
</P>
<P>
The nation should proceed in doing everything from the actual
conditions of the primary stage of socialism, and not from this or
that kind of foreign models, nor from some certain Marxist theses,
it says.
</P>
<P>
Deng Xiaoping Theory has incisively expounded the essence and
the development law of socialism, the article says.
