<HEADLINE> Signed Article on Scientific Truth of Deng Xiaoping Theory (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Deng Xiaoping Theory has helped the people know what socialism
is and how to build it, it says.
</P>
<P>
One of the fundamental reasons for the nation's failures in
building socialism prior to the Third Plenary Session of the
Eleventh CPC Central Committee in 1978 is that some of its tasks and
policies overstepped the primary stage of socialism, the article
states.
</P>
<P>
Only following Deng Xiaoping Theory can China bring about a
great rejuvenation, it states.
</P>
<P>
Deng Xiaoping Theory is Marxism of present-day China,
representing a new development stage of Marxism, the article says.
</P>
<P>
The theory has upheld the principles of emancipating the mind and
seeking truth from facts, while inheriting and developing Marxism.
</P>
<P>
In China today, it is Deng Xiaoping Theory which integrates
Marxism with the practice of present-day China and only this
theory can settle the issues concerning the future and destiny of
socialism.
</P>
<P>
In addition, the theory, persisting in observing the world in
the broad perspective of Marxism, has made new, scientific
judgments on the basis of correctly analyzing the features of the
times and the overall international situation.
</P>
<P>
Furthermore, Deng Xiaoping Theory constitutes a new, scientific
system of the theory of building socialism with Chinese
characteristics, it says. 
</P>
