Burkina Faso to see what are the opportunities so that when we are
better off we can go (and invest) there."
</P>
<P>
Briefing reporters about the meeting, Malaysian Foreign
Minister Abdullah Ahmad Badawi said among the possible sectors for
cooperation were telecommunications, agriculture, air services,
the automotive industry and mining.
</P>
<P>
Compaore arrived Wednesday for a five-day visit to Malaysia.
