promoted into the first division league, finished seventh in the
last season and took the indoor title of the German Football
Association in 1996.
</P>
<P>
The Czech Republic also dispatched its top-notch squad to the
tournament, composed of members of the Olympic squad and three
national footers, while Rampla Junior contributed its members to
the national squad and even to the Pan-American United Team, the
organizers said.
</P>
<P>
