acts were alien to the sentiments of the Greek people and did harm
to the country.
</P>
<P>
Greece has witnessed a 20-30 percent surge in violent crimes
this year and the government has committed more men, money and
more help from the armed forces to help police beat the surge in
violent crimes. 
