<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 23 (Xinhua) -- The executive vice-president of
the Association for Relations Across the Taiwan Straits (ARATS),
Tang Shubei, said here today that the chairman of the Taiwan
Straits Exchange Foundation (SEF), Koo Chen-fu, is welcome here to
take part in activities or symposiums the two organizations hold.
</P>
<P>
He said that the ARATS and SEF discussions today is helpful for
Mr. Koo's visit.
</P>
<P>
Tang and the secretary general of ARATS, Zhang Jincheng, met
this afternoon with an SEF group led by SEF's deputy-secretary
general, Jan Jyh-horng. SEF expressed the hope that mr. Koo
Chen-fu could visit the mainland within this year.
</P>
<P>
