located in the Pacific Region and noted that both have enjoyed
rapid economic development for more than 10 years
</P>
<P>
The two countries should take advantage of enhanced conditions
for cooperation and exchanges, and should seize the excellent
opportunity to fully develop bilateral relations, according to
Jiang.
</P>
<P>
Lagos said that Chile was one of the first South American
countries to establish diplomatic ties with China and has closely
followed the nation's development and changes.
</P>
<P>
He said he was highly impressed with the vitality of the
Chinese economy and agreed that the Asia-Pacific Region is the
most economically vigorous region in the world. He said Chile is
fully prepared to enhance cooperation with China and help promote
the region's economic development.
</P>
<P>
Lagos is on his first visit to China at the invitation of the
International Department of the CPC Central Committee. 
