<TEXT>
<P>
TIANJIN, April 23 (Xinhua) -- The world-famous American
machinery giant, Caterpillar Co., has chosen Tianjin, a north
China city, as its engineering equipment production base.
</P>
<P>
Duane E. Devore, a senior representative from Caterpillar, said
that the company is building its only caterpillar tread plant in
the city's Bonded Zone which involves a total investment of 40
million US dollars.
</P>
