Province, President Jiang Zemin has urged local governments to
fully support the development of township-run enterprises,
stressing that developing township enterprises is an important
strategy and a long-term, fundamental policy of China.
</P>
<P>
"Xinhua Daily Telegraph"
</P>
<P>
