yesterday that the Chinese Communist Party and the Government are
confident of solving the employment problem for urban people and
will certainly bel able to establish a social security system with
Chinese characteristics.
</P>
<P>
-- The paper devoted half a page to an article hailing the
glorious history of Beijing University which is to celebrate its
centennial on May 4, and its remarkable achievements in fostering
qualified people in various fields and great contributions to the
development of China's education, science and culture as well as
modernization drive over the past 100 years.
</P>
<P>
-- People from all walks of life in the Chinese capital
attended a series of activities yesterday to mark the 28th World
Earth Day. The theme of China's activities marking the special day
is "maritime geology and mankind", calling on people to pay
attention to maritime protection.
</P>
<P>
"China Daily"
</P>
<P>
